Torrance Refining Company LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 9:39 PM ET
Oil, Gas and Consumable Fuels

Company Overview of Torrance Refining Company LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Torrance Refining Company LLC provides crude oil refining services. The company offers gasoline, diesel fuel, jet fuel, liquefied petroleum gases, coke, and sulfur. It provides its products through a series of pipelines and terminals for use in fueling cars, trucks, buses, trains, boats, planes, and others. The company was incorporated in 2015 and is based in Parsippany, New Jersey. Torrance Refining Company LLC operates as a subsidiary of PBF Energy Western Region LLC.


One Sylvan WaySecond FloorParsippany, NJ 07054United StatesFounded in 2015



Phone: 310-505-3158

www.torrancerefinery.com







